<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037844" n="1"/> 
    <opener><salute><lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-140736662">F. C.</rs> Amico suo <abbr>pl.</abbr> colendo <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nic. Bern.</rs></salute></opener>
    <p><rs type="letter">Literas</rs> tuas suavissimas mihi reddidit <rs type="person">Tobias Thurnisiorum</rs> <rs type="person">famulus</rs>, per quem nunc ex nundi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nis <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileam</rs> redeuntem responsorias tibi mittere fas est, libentius quidem ego ipse eum comi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tatus essem, sed fata me alio iter dirigere jubent; quanquam igitur su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o cum gaudio hinc
<lb/>discedam, non minorem tamen quam tu sentio dolorem, eo quod <add>mihi</add> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia tua charissi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ma diutius, quam ab initio speravi, carendum est; quemadmodum vero utrique nostrum
<lb/>eadem est causa doloris, ita me idem quod te erigit solatium, quod <abbr>sc.</abbr> Deus omnia numine
<lb/>suo regat, hic nos citius, quam putamus, iterum conjungere poterit; illud etiam non parum
        <lb/>mihi solatio fuit, quod nuntiasti te hoc anno <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> mansurum, ita enim spes est, posse
<lb/>me absoluto per <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>statem itinere meo ante h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>emem <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>nisi singulare quid hoc impediat<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> do<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mum reverti tuaque exoptatissima frui pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia. Optime agis quod <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-116082356">Battierium</rs> non
<lb/>nisi in Collegiis Disputatoriis frequentas, poteris enim perquam bene <rs type="keyword">Jus Feudale</rs> et <rs type="keyword">Canonic<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>,
<lb/>ut ipse <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Doctor</rs> tibi suasit et ego etiam feci, domi pertractare; suaderem tibi, ut te quam<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>primum Examini subjiceres, et demum post Examen Disputationi conscribend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> operam dares.
<lb/>Quinque<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ium integrum studio Juris impendendum esse nunquam audivi, sed semper existima<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>vi, aliquem ad Examen recipi, si quintum a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>um inceperit. Miror <abbr>D.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Battierium</rs> ita occu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>patum esse tali tempore, quo tam parvus est studiosorum Juris numerus. <date>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terito die Solis</date> <abbr>D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs type="person">Bonif. Feschio</rs> dubio procul Rectoris, et tibi Consistorialis munus delatum est, quod si ita est, ti<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>bi gratulor. <abbr>D.os</abbr> Professores <rs type="person">Werenfelsium</rs>, <rs type="person">Buxtorfium</rs> et <rs type="person">Iselium</rs> in <rs type="organisation">Gallico templo</rs> conciona<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tos esse, et prioris concionem impressum iri, hic audivi; quanta cum vehementia <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Iselius</rs> in
<lb/>vitia hominum insurrexerit, bene mihi imaginari possum, memini enim illum in <rs type="organisation">Templo Pe<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>trino</rs> olim tempore <date>Paschatis</date> super eundem <rs type="biblio">Textum</rs> concionatum et ita debacchatum esse,
<lb/>ut plurimi hoc indigne tulerint, credo itaque eum eandem illam concionem in Gallicum 
<pb facs="1037845" n="2"/> 
<lb/>sermonem versam recitasse. Jam demum certum est, quod <rs type="organisation">Bernenses</rs> nullam Professionem Juris
        <lb/>hic constituent, qua de causa <abbr>D.</abbr> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-128694416">Waldkirch</rs>, qui hucusque semper aliquid spei habuit, bre<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>vi tempore <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileam</rs> revertetur. <date>Nudius tertius</date> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Fattet</rs> per <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bernam</rs> transiit, mecumque de
<lb/>te et conditione tibi apud certum <abbr>D.</abbr> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Wattenw<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>l</rs> comparanda verba fecit, sed nescio, an
<lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> re tua sit ejusmodi conditiones accipere, idque certas ob causas, de quibus Deo volente ali<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>quando coram dicendi locus erit. Mihi quoque interea plures oblat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fuerunt conditiones, imo
<lb/>ipse Consul <rs type="person">Willadingius</rs>, qui volebat, ut generi sui <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Generalis ab Erlach</rs> et hodierni pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>fecti in <rs type="place">Aarwangen</rs> <rs type="person">filios</rs> instruerem, hanc ob rem ad <rs type="person">Patrem</rs> meum scribi curavit, sed ego
<lb/>hanc conditionem et c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teras omnes recusavi existimans, satius esse, ut meis potius quam
<lb/>ali<del/><add>orum</add> studiis invigilem. <date>Proximo die Lun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></date> aut <date>Martis</date> hinc proficiscar, et quamprimum
        <lb/><rs type="place">Genevam</rs>, ubi forte eodem, quo <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Raillardus</rs>, hospitio utar, venero, tibi scribam.</p> <closer>Vale. <lb/><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-05-10">10. Maji 1710</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript>
<p><lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Iniquum mihi videtur esse, ut semper de Mathematicis
<lb/>rebus sileamus, quapropter ut habeamus quo nos exercere possimus, sequens tibi propono
<lb/>Problema: Invenire su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>am talis seriei, cujus singuli termini sunt quadrata singulorum
<lb/>terminorum cujuscunque Progressionis Arithmetic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. <abbr>Ex. gr.</abbr> in hac Progressione Arithme<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tica <formula>2. 5. 8. 11.</formula><space unit="nbsp"/><choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ritur quid centum primorum terminorum quadrata in unam
<lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>am collecta efficiant?</p>
</postscript>
</div>
